  "prompt": "Where can I get very reasonable price for men's shoes in Sydney?",
  "response": "In Sydney, there are several places where you can find men's shoes at reasonable prices:\n\n1. **Discount Shoe Stores**: Stores like **Schuh**, **The Athlete's Foot**, and **Vincent's** often have sales and carry a range of brands at discounted prices.\n\n2. **Factory Outlets**: Visit outlet stores in areas like Homebush (DFO) or Liverpool. Here, you can find past season stock at significantly reduced prices.\n\n3. **Department Stores**: Check out large department stores such as **David Jones** and **Myer**, which frequently have sales, especially during seasonal sales periods.\n\n4. **Online Retailers**: Websites like **ASOS**, **Zalora**, and **THE ICONIC** often have competitive prices and regular discounts on men\u2019s shoes.\n\n5. **Local Markets**: Markets like the **Paddy's Markets** in Haymarket can have affordable options from various vendors.\n\n6. **Thrift Stores**: Check out second-hand stores or charity shops, such as **Salvation Army** or **Oxfam**, for gently used shoes at lower prices.\n\n7. **Specialty Shoe Stores**: Stores like **Hype DC** or **Foot Locker** may also have sales or clearance sections.\n\nBe sure to watch for sales events, particularly during holidays and end-of-season sales, to get the best deals on men's shoes.",
